2026-04-19 | Check if y is a Power of x

Question
Return true if y is a power of x, else false.
	Approach (Preferred: Iterative Division)
1.	Handle edge cases:
		if x == 1:
			return y == 1  
2.	While y is divisible by x:
		y /= x  
3.	If y becomes 1 → return true  
	else → return false  
	Time Complexity
	O(logₓ y)
	Space Complexity
	O(1)
	Solution
class Solution {
public:
    bool isPower(int x, int y) {
        if(x == 1) return y == 1;
        while(y % x == 0){
            y /= x;
        }
        return y == 1;
    }
};
	Key Insight
If y is a power of x:
		you can repeatedly divide y by x until it becomes 1.  
If at any point it’s not divisible → not a power.
